{"id":150813,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/东盟峰会未能解决泰柬边境冲突/","date":"2011-05-08T16:00:20Z","modified":"2011-05-08T16:00:20Z","title":"东盟峰会未能解决泰柬边境冲突","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">雅加达</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">东南亚国家联盟未能在本年度峰会上找到谈判解决泰国和柬埔寨之间边界冲突的途径。在峰会周日（</span><span>5</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span><span>8</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日）发表的结束声明中，东盟国家要求峰会东道主印尼政府继续斡旋。声明称，应根据东盟团结精神友好解决冲突。会议对东盟今年</span><span>2</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月作出的关于印尼观察员进入有争议边境地区的决定表示欢迎，并要求印尼继续斡旋努力。在印尼总统苏西洛的调解下，泰国总理阿披实和柬埔寨总理洪森今天举行了双边会晤，但未能获得突破性进展。不过，两国外长下周一将继续在雅加达磋商解决争端。泰柬两国之间数周以来发生激烈边界冲突，导致</span><span>18</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人丧生，并一度造成大约</span><span>8.5</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万人背井离乡。两国之间的边界线有多处段落未清晰划分，尤其是对帕威夏神庙的主权争议，导致两国间发生长达数十年的外交纠纷。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15059456%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E4%B8%9C%E7%9B%9F%E5%B3%B0%E4%BC%9A%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%B3%B0%E6%9F%AC%E8%BE%B9%E5%A2%83%E5%86%B2%E7%AA%81\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" v